	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can make .nsf with NerdTracker II or Famitracker, but you can't "just convert a MIDI file" yet. You can convert .nsf to .wav using Winamp with any NSF input plug-in and the Disk Writer output plug-in.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


